caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on August 08, 2021 tagging @mercedesamg, and @theshmeemobiles. May be an image of car.
text: It's time! @theshmeemobiles AMG GT Black Series is being resprayed AMG Solarbeam Yellow, and I cannot wait to see how it looks. This was always the plan hence the choice of Graphite Grey Magno for the base as it's the easiest to work with. The transformation is being done by @chartwell_derby just as per my SLS BS respray to Mystic Blue and the repairs to my Senna before. Why not just order it like this you say? It wasn't an option, and believe me I tried. It was absolutely impossible to order the car (RHD UK allocation) in anything other than the standard 8 choices available so this is the only way. What about the value? Life is too short, I'm going to do many thousands of miles in this car for many years to come, reselling it is not in the plans. #Mercedes #AMG #GTBlackSeries #Shmeemobile #Shmee150
